metadata.name: Magic Key
metadata.description: Introducing Magic Key - the revolutionary NFT project that unlocks access to Home Renovation Nation's cutting-edge SaaS application! With Magic Key, field service professionals gain exclusive entry to a world of game-changing tools and resources, empowering them to take their home renovation skills to the next level. This open edition NFT is the key to unlocking a world of endless possibilities - don't miss your chance to be a part of the magic!
